        "Target": "\u30EA\u30AA\u30EC\u30A6\u30B9\uFF11\u982D\u3068\r\n\u30C6\u30A3\u30AC\u30EC\u30C3\u30AF\u30B9\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "King of the Sky, Bane of the Land",
        "Client": "Young General",
        "Description": "My subordinates had enough of\r\ntheir harsh missions and\r\nrebelled. I was forced to take\r\nresponsibility and demoted to\r\nthe Lava Caverns. I need to get\r\nbetter at my job, but to do so\r\nI need to survive first! Help!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Rathalos and a Tigrex",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Roi des Cieux, fl\u00E9au sur terre",
        "Client": "Jeune g\u00E9n\u00E9ral",
        "Description": "Mes subordonn\u00E9s trouvaient\r\nleurs missions trop dures et se\r\nsont rebell\u00E9s. J\u0027ai \u00E9t\u00E9 d\u00E9chu\r\nde mes fonctions et j\u0027ai d\u00FB\r\nprendre un poste aux Cavernes.\r\nJe dois m\u0027am\u00E9liorer, mais il\r\nfaut d\u0027abord que je survive !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Rathalos et un Tigrex",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Distruttori di cielo e terra",
        "Client": "Giovane generale",
        "Description": "I miei sottoposti erano stufi\r\ndi missioni cos\u00EC dure e si\r\nsono ribellati. Ho dovuto\r\nassumermi la responsabilit\u00E0 e\r\nretrocedere alle Caverne\r\nlaviche. Migliorer\u00F2, ma prima\r\ndevo sopravvivere! Aiuto!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Rathalos e un Tigrex",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Himmelsk\u00F6nig und Landplage",
        "Client": "Junger General",
        "Description": "Meine Untergebenen hatten ihre\r\nbrutalen Missionen satt und\r\nhaben rebelliert. Ich wurde in\r\ndie Lavah\u00F6hlen strafversetzt.\r\nIch will ein besserer General\r\nwerden, aber dazu muss ich\r\nerst mal \u00FCberleben. Hilfe!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Rathalos und einen Tigrex.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "El rey azota la tierra",
        "Client": "Joven general",
        "Description": "Mis subordinados se rebelaron,\r\nhartos de misiones dif\u00EDciles.\r\nMe han hecho responsable y\r\ndestinado a las Grutas de\r\nlava. Necesito mejorar en mi\r\ntrabajo, \u00A1pero antes debo\r\nsobrevivir! \u00A1Ayuda!",
        "Target": "Caza un Rathalos y un Tigrex",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041A\u043E\u0440\u043E\u043B\u044C \u041D\u0435\u0431\u0435\u0441, \u0413\u0440\u043E\u0437\u0430 \u0417\u0435\u043C\u0435\u043B\u044C",
        "Client": "\u041C\u043E\u043B\u043E\u0434\u043E\u0439 \u043F\u043E\u043B\u043A\u043E\u0432\u043E\u0434\u0435\u0446",
        "Description": "\u041C\u043E\u0438 \u0441\u043E\u043B\u0434\u0430\u0442\u044B \u043D\u0435 \u0432\u044B\u043D\u0435\u0441\u043B\u0438 \u0442\u044F\u0436\u0435\u043B\u044B\u0445\r\n\u0437\u0430\u0434\u0430\u043D\u0438\u0439 \u0438 \u0432\u0437\u0431\u0443\u043D\u0442\u043E\u0432\u0430\u043B\u0438\u0441\u044C.\r\n\u042F \u0432\u044B\u043D\u0443\u0436\u0434\u0435\u043D \u0431\u044B\u043B \u0432\u0437\u044F\u0442\u044C \u043D\u0430 \u0441\u0435\u0431\u044F\r\n\u043E\u0442\u0432\u0435\u0442\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043D\u043D\u043E\u0441\u0442\u044C \u0438 \u043E\u0442\u043F\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0438\u043B\u0441\u044F\r\n\u0432 \u041B\u0430\u0432\u043E\u0432\u044B\u0435 \u043F\u0435\u0449\u0435\u0440\u044B. \u041C\u043D\u0435 \u043D\u0443\u0436\u043D\u043E\r\n\u0441\u043B\u0443\u0436\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0435\u0449\u0435 \u043B\u0443\u0447\u0448\u0435, \u043D\u043E \u0434\u043B\u044F\r\n\u044D\u0442\u043E\u0433\u043E \u043D\u0430\u0434\u043E \u043E\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F \u0432 \u0436\u0438\u0432\u044B\u0445!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0420\u0430\u0442\u0430\u043B\u043E\u0441\u0430 \u0438 \u0422\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0435\u043A\u0441\u0430",
